Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • interpreter.Command
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommandAdd, CommandDelete, CommandHelp, CommandSearchName, CommandSearchTime, CommandUpdate, CommandView

    public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to create command objects with command type and arguments. Super-class of CommandAdd, CommandDelete, CommandUpdate, CommandView and CommandUndo.

    SP
